      "raw_text": "People of Byrne's addition have\nentered a protest against granting\nthe Washington Water Power Co. a\nfranchise for \"Y\" track at the\npresent terminus Of the Division\nstreet line, at Rowe avenue, unless\nthe company agrees to extend its\nline a half mile farther north, to\nByrne's addition.\n\n\n1t is proposed by the Washington\nWater Power Co. to locate \"Y''\ntracks at the ends of all of its lines\nin order to enable it to turn its\ncars, instead of reversing end for\nend as at present When the \"Ys\"\nare Installed it is proposed to in\naugurate pay as you enter\" plan\nof collecting fares."
